This is an example application of my blog post:

Spring from the Trenches: Invoking a Secured Method From a Scheduled Job

http://www.petrikainulainen.net/programming/spring-framework/spring-from-the-trenches-invoking-a-secured-method-from-a-scheduled-job/

NOTE: The XML configuration is not working at the moment.

RUNNING THE APPLICATION:

You can run the application by running the following command at command prompt:

mvn clean jetty:run -P dev (development profile)
mvn clean jetty:run -P prod (production profile)

